{"topic_title": "[MagaLu] Monitor Dell S3422DWG 34\" UQHD 1440p Painel VA Curvo 144Hz 2ms Free/Gsync 3 anos de garantia - R$ 4504,72 - Frete Gr\u00e1tis.", "topic_url": "/threads/magalu-monitor-dell-s3422dwg-34-uqhd-1440p-painel-va-curvo-144hz-2ms-free-gsync-3-anos-de-garantia-r-4504-72-frete-gratis.689895/", "author": "Chackall", "author_url": "/members/chackall.215000/", "creation_date": "1637603772", "comments": "29", "views": "4K", "first_post": "<div class=\"bbWrapper\"><div class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--unfurl    js-unfurl fauxBlockLink\" data-unfurl=\"true\" data-result-id=\"205848\" data-url=\"https://www.magazineluiza.com.br/monitor-dell-curvo-wqhd-34-s3422dwg-preto/p/cf9j64dhd6/in/mogm/?&amp;seller_id=dell&amp;utm_source=google&amp;utm_medium=pla&amp;utm_campaign=&amp;partner_id=58961&amp;&amp;&amp;utm_source=google&amp;utm_medium=pla&amp;utm_campaign=&amp;partner_id=58961&amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMIpY-Z6MCs9AIVBAiRCh1DrQipEAQYASABEgLNj_D_BwE&amp;gclsrc=aw.ds\" data-host=\"www.magazineluiza.com.br\" data-pending=\"false\">\n<div class=\"contentRow\">\n<div class=\"contentRow-figure contentRow-figure--fixedSmall js-unfurl-figure\">\n<img src=\"https://a-static.mlcdn.com.br/undefinedxundefined/monitor-dell-curvo-wqhd-34-s3422dwg-preto/dell/ms3422dwg/46c35941454201a80817d091e90d93c5.jpg\" alt=\"www.magazineluiza.com.br\" data-onerror=\"hide-parent\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"contentRow-main\">\n<h3 class=\"contentRow-header js-unfurl-title\">\n<a href=\"https://www.magazineluiza.com.br/monitor-dell-curvo-wqhd-34-s3422dwg-preto/p/cf9j64dhd6/in/mogm/?&amp;seller_id=dell&amp;utm_source=google&amp;utm_medium=pla&amp;utm_campaign=&amp;partner_id=58961&amp;&amp;&amp;utm_source=google&amp;utm_medium=pla&amp;utm_campaign=&amp;partner_id=58961&amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMIpY-Z6MCs9AIVBAiRCh1DrQipEAQYASABEgLNj_D_BwE&amp;gclsrc=aw.ds\" class=\"link link--external fauxBlockLink-blockLink\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-proxy-href=\"\">\nMonitor Dell Curvo WQHD 34\" S3422DWG Preto - Monitor Gamer - Magazine Luiza\n</a>\n</h3>\n<div class=\"contentRow-snippet js-unfurl-desc\">Monitor Dell Curvo WQHD 34\" S3422DWG Preto com as melhores condi\u00e7\u00f5es voc\u00ea encontra no site do Magalu. Confira!</div>\n<div class=\"contentRow-minor contentRow-minor--hideLinks\">\n<span class=\"js-unfurl-favicon\">\n<img src=\"https://wx.mlcdn.com.br/site/shared/favicon/favicon-16x16.png\" alt=\"www.magazineluiza.com.br\" class=\"bbCodeBlockUnfurl-icon\" data-onerror=\"hide-parent\">\n</span>\nwww.magazineluiza.com.br\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br>\nEsta saindo por <b>R$ 4.504,72</b> \u00e0 vista com Frete Gr\u00e1tis (pelo menos pra minha regi\u00e3o) e 3 anos de garantia. Um dos menores pre\u00e7os nos \u00faltimos 6 meses.<br>\n<br>\nReview da Rtings:<br>\n<br>\n<div class=\"bbCodeBlock bbCodeBlock--unfurl    js-unfurl fauxBlockLink\" data-unfurl=\"true\" data-result-id=\"205851\" data-url=\"https://www.rtings.com/monitor/reviews/dell/s3422dwg\" data-host=\"www.rtings.com\" data-pending=\"false\">\n<div class=\"contentRow\">\n<div class=\"contentRow-figure contentRow-figure--fixedSmall js-unfurl-figure\">\n<img src=\"https://i.rtings.com/assets/products/6RDCghNf/dell-s3422dwg/design-medium.jpg\" alt=\"www.rtings.com\" data-onerror=\"hide-parent\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"contentRow-main\">\n<h3 class=\"contentRow-header js-unfurl-title\">\n<a href=\"https://www.rtings.com/monitor/reviews/dell/s3422dwg\" class=\"link link--external fauxBlockLink-blockLink\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-proxy-href=\"\">\nDell S3422DWG Review\n</a>\n</h3>\n<div class=\"contentRow-snippet js-unfurl-desc\">The Dell S3422DWG is a very good 34 inch 1440p ultrawide monitor with a VA panel. It has good contrast and great black uniformity, so it looks great in a dark ro...</div>\n<div class=\"contentRow-minor contentRow-minor--hideLinks\">\n<span class=\"js-unfurl-favicon\">\n<img src=\"https://i.rtings.com/assets/favicon/current/android-icon-192x192-2c57e3c2e187fc221f412f51391e49f0b619c4f733a84ffc5ad4a4df85aa1238.png\" alt=\"www.rtings.com\" class=\"bbCodeBlockUnfurl-icon\" data-onerror=\"hide-parent\">\n</span>\nwww.rtings.com\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br>\nEstou 'namorando' esse monitor h\u00e1 meses para substituir meu X34 Predator. N\u00e3o vi nenhuma an\u00e1lise deixando de recomendar o monitor. Praticamente todas afirmavam que \u00e9 o melhor custo benef\u00edcio da categoria. Apesar do painel em VA, se utilizado com o tempo de resposta em Super Fast praticamente n\u00e3o apresenta ghosting ou smearing. Esses problemas come\u00e7am a aparecer apensa com o tempo de resposta em Extreme.<br>\n<br>\nApesar de divulgar apenas o FreeSync, o Gsync tamb\u00e9m funciona nele, por\u00e9m n\u00e3o responde bem para jogos que caem de 60fps, causando smearing na tela, ent\u00e3o se o cidad\u00e3o n\u00e3o tem uma m\u00e1quina que mantenha sempre acima dos 60fps, \u00e9 um contra a se considerar.</div>"}
